# Project Context: PoseMaster (gesture-practice)

This is the **PoseMaster desktop app** for gesture/figure drawing practice.

## Wrong Project Detection

If the user asks about any of the following topics, they are likely in the wrong Cursor window:

- dahligarciamarquez
- personal website
- blog posts
- Supabase auth (unless specifically about this project)
- Vercel deployment
- blog styling
- website navbar
- contact page
- about page
- posts/articles

**When detected**: Politely remind the user:
> "It looks like you're asking about your website, but we're currently in the PoseMaster project window. Would you like to switch to the website workspace?"

Then wait for confirmation before proceeding.
